{
  "stem": "14613.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were like together in one place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the next thing after the few days traveling-- and we did not know exactly how long where we go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All we knew is that we are-- the train is going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We knew the train is stopping.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We could feel the train goes back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We felt the train is being connected somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We see the movements.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We hear the movements.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Where we go, we don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, the next thing I remember is suddenly the cattle car doors opened with a force.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we hear tremendous noise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's really wrong to say noise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's a combination of sounds-- of crying women, crying children, yelling, giving orders, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] dog barkings, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and the light which struck us when they opened the door.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because in a way, after a few days we-- we were, call it, accustomed to the darkness.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So that the opening of the doors created like a lightning to us-- we could hardly see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So the noise is the first thing that we could hear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we slowly started to distinguish the noise and the commands, [SPEAKING GERMAN], everybody to get out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And as we were walking out, the thing which struck me is the noise multiplied.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The barkings of the dogs became louder, the crying of the women and the children penetrate the air.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we started to see-- not only to hear, but to see what's going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The masses of people being pushed, being beaten by people standing, by Germans sitting on horses, beating them and yelling.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Forwards, go, go, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also have seen-- and this was maybe the first time when I really encountered the-- the actual brutality.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
